body:
Hello!  
My name is Cory A. Kendall.  
I am a student at Saint Vincent College in Latrobe, PA, where I am majoring in Politics. I have started this website to introduce people to me, and to help me further my career eventually.

If you need to contact me, please do so by emailing me at: cory@coryakendall.me
